# hyperhdr-py

- **PyPI**: `hyperhdr-py-sickkick` — **import**: `hyperhdr` (not the PyPI name).
- **Repo**: https://github.com/sickkick/hyperhdr-py — use this for README/raw links, not legacy fork URLs.
- **Scope**: Python client for HyperHDR JSON API; extends hyperion-py. API shapes: https://docs.hyperhdr-project.org/en/json/ — methods live in `hyperhdr/client.py` as `async_*`.
- **Streaming**: `hyperhdr.stream`; optional extras `[stream]` / `[stream-jpeg]`.
- **Tooling**: Poetry, pytest. Longer context: **AGENTS.md**.
